This folder holds a number of matlab, bash, and HPC submission scripts
that can be used as is or as examples for modification.

anelastic_benchmark.m	: matlab script to generate "planet_model.txt.in"
diffus_model.m		: matlab script to generate "diffusivity.txt"
jup_model_finalsmooth2_paper.m : matlab script to generate input parameters for 
                                 French et al 2012
run.bolt		: example submission script for ARCHER2
sub.sh			: example submission script for ARC4 at University of Leeds	
